      <div class="prose">

        <p>Buildertrend and UDA ConstructionOnline are both solid choices for custom homebuilders and remodelers. Buildertrend is the dominant market player with a more polished UX. ConstructionOnline competes on estimating depth and specification writing. This comparison breaks down where each platform wins.</p>

        <h2>Quick comparison</h2>
        <div class="quick-table">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr><th></th><th>Buildertrend</th><th>Construction Online</th></tr>
            </thead>
